+6. Limitation of Liability:
+IN NO EVENT SHALL THE LICENSOR BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF PROFITS OR REVENUE, WHETHER INCURRED DIRECTLY OR INDIRECTLY, ARISING FROM YOUR USE OF THIS LICENSE AND ITS ASSOCIATED SYSTEM. YOU ARE USING THE LICENSED MATERIAL AT YOUR OWN RISK. THE LICENSOR’S LIABILITY, IS LIMITED TO ONLY THE AMOUNT THAT IS PAID IN TOKEN FORM BY THE LICENSEE FOR THE USAGE OF THE SYSTEM.
+7. Termination:
+This License will terminate automatically if the Licensee fails to comply with any of the terms and conditions of this license, or as defined in the MTL Parameter Addendum. This includes, but not limited to: invalid usage, not maintaining minimum required tokens, incomplete reports, and non-payment of dues.
+8. Entire Agreement:
